                <li><strong>Validate:</strong> Check if audio streams smoothly from TV to phone over WiFi</li>
            </ol>
            
            <div class="connection-info">
                <strong>üìã MVP Validation Goals:</strong><br>
                ‚úÖ Prove WebRTC can stream audio over local WiFi<br>
                ‚úÖ Test latency and quality with real content<br>
                ‚úÖ Identify technical challenges and limitations<br>
                ‚úÖ Validate user experience and feasibility
            </div>
